{"tid":2158842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那要求漁民不要靠近釣魚台","createTime":"2020-08-16T03:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T08:07:28.000Z","uid":50386,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0d05ac9e5da42ee0a9a9541fefd3fb02d90ae1a6","tid":2158842,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】日本傳媒報道，中國福建及浙江省有關部門要求漁民在休漁期結束後，不要靠近釣魚島周邊範圍捕魚作業，避免與日本發生摩擦。 <br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，中國在尖閣諸島，即中方所稱的釣魚島周邊海域，設置的休漁期於今天結束，日本政府已通過外交渠道向中方提出交涉，要求防止有中國漁船進入釣魚島周邊的日本領海。<br />\n<br />\n有中國漁民就表示，福建及浙江兩省有關部門已要求他們在恢復捕魚作業後，不要進入釣魚島周邊三十海里以內範圍。在福建的石獅市漁港掛上了嚴禁漁船到敏感海域捕撈作業的橫幅。<br />\n<br />\n據報，中國有關部門會使用衛星定位系統監控漁船位置。有分析指，雖然中國加強擁有釣魚島主權的主張，但仍然不想日本發生過度摩擦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401901&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401901%26refer%3DShare&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=d9f55af7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401901%26refer%3DShare&h=3c6c3fb3\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401901&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n支共：釣魚台是中國的<br />\n但你哋唔可以去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab8047658ffd908df7ad186e814d6a3a43a4586","tid":2158842,"uid":77104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576b06a68fd81662dd5fb0bdd17e466e38edad9f","tid":2158842,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"又縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076ad0d3f54af5d78e3bfc31d307ae937f3b78ee","tid":2158842,"uid":259674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091ef78b85d0a78f1ce6191b21c28fb04d4b8459","tid":2158842,"uid":23635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"不是一點也不能少嗎？"},{"pid":"db2828b314241a4dadde0a6247be42009964602b","tid":2158842,"uid":17103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"一個島都唔敢要, 我想知你點吞台灣."},{"pid":"91cd6327b2bb597edea605f5bf0da4ccbff77045","tid":2158842,"uid":310853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"全宇宙都是中國的"},{"pid":"c6153e771dacda66a460281631a210c7f46e7510","tid":2158842,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:36:07.000Z","msg":"後果自付?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1820e8a4fe19c3e358c33952c7fcf10fd60dd0","tid":2158842,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:38:54.000Z","msg":"縮國"},{"pid":"6eedd8c4f4c1ef60e8d9b71f7c8723e51991506a","tid":2158842,"uid":35585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"中国一點也不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f535cdbd3faf1480245e8e9656a0c152925bf90","tid":2158842,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eedd8c4f4c1ef60e8d9b71f7c8723e51991506a","tid":2158842,"uid":35585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"中国一點也不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:40:36.000Z","msg":"釣魚台除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6761609203647574b1e9c24413a507f3e2bc2286","tid":2158842,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db2828b314241a4dadde0a6247be42009964602b","tid":